'''Colossal Order''' 是一家芬兰[[游戏制作|游戏制作]]公司，因制作[[模拟经营游戏|模拟经营游戏]][[都市运输系列|都市运输系列]]和[[城市建造游戏|城市建造游戏]]《[[都市：天际线|都市：天际线]]》而知名<ref name="rps_cim_impressions">{{cite web|url=http://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2011/01/05/impressions-cities-in-motion/|title=Some Impressions: Cities in Motion|accessdate=12 March 2015|author=Quintin Smith|date=5 January 2011|publisher=[[Rock,_Paper,_Shotgun|Rock, Paper, Shotgun]]|archive-date=2015-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150408010017/http://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2011/01/05/impressions-cities-in-motion/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="rps_cim2_announced">{{cite web|url=http://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2012/08/15/on-the-buses-cities-in-motion-2/|title=On the Buses: Cities in Motion 2|accessdate=12 March 2015|author=John Walker|date=15 August 2012|publisher=[[Rock,_Paper,_Shotgun|Rock, Paper, Shotgun]]|archive-date=2015-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402123938/http://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2012/08/15/on-the-buses-cities-in-motion-2/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="rps_skylines_review">{{cite web|url=http://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2015/03/10/cities-skylines-review/|title=Wot I Think: Cities: Skylines|accessdate=12 March 2015|author=Alec Meer|date=10 March 2015|publisher=[[Rock,_Paper,_Shotgun|Rock, Paper, Shotgun]]|archive-date=2015-03-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150311160327/http://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2015/03/10/cities-skylines-review/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="company">{{cite web|url=http://www.colossalorder.fi/company.html|title=Company|accessdate=10 March 2015|work=Colossal Order|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150307191817/http://www.colossalorder.fi/company.html|archivedate=2015年3月7日}}</ref>。公司于2009年在[[芬兰|芬兰]][[坦佩雷|坦佩雷]]建立。它的发行商是 [[Paradox_Interactive|Paradox Interactive]]<ref name="gamereactor">{{Cite web|url=http://www.gamereactor.fi/artikkelit/80006/Esittelyss%E4+Colossal+Order/|title=Esittelyssä Colossal Order|date=17 March 2011|last=Mika Sorvari|work=Gamereactor Finland|publisher=Gamez Publishing A/S|language=fi|trans-title=Introducing Colossal Order|access-date=5 March 2015}}</ref>，Colossal Order的所有游戏由Paradox负责测试、销售、分发。公司的CEO为Mariina Hallikainen<ref name="finder">{{Cite web|url=http://www.finder.fi/IT-sovelluksia,%20IT-ohjelmistoja/Colossal%20Order%20Oy/TAMPERE/paattajat/2154618|title=Vastuuhenkilöt|date=|last=|work=|publisher=Fonecta Finder|language=fi|trans-title=Responsibilities|access-date=5 March 2015|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304080626/http://www.finder.fi/IT-sovelluksia,%20IT-ohjelmistoja/Colossal%20Order%20Oy/TAMPERE/paattajat/2154618|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
